quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  104,4,"Nay! Verily, he will be thrown into the crushing Fire."
  104,5,"And what will make you know what the crushing Fire is?"
  104,6,"The fire of Allâh kindled,"
  105,1,"Have you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) not seen how your Lord dealt with the owners of the Elephant? [The Elephant army which came from Yemen under the command of Abrahah Al-Ashram intending to destroy the Ka‘bah at Makkah]."
  105,2,"Did He not make their plot go astray?"
  105,3,"And He sent against them birds, in flocks,"